OL,3,CMum of man with schizophrenia who
OL,4,Ckilled grandfather say care failings
OL,5,Cpersist
OL,7,FThe family of a man who had
OL,8,Fschizophrenia and killed his
OL,9,Fgrandfather, have hit out at the
OL,10,Fhealth trust responsible for his care
OL,11,Ffor failing to learn lessons from the
OL,12,Fcase.
OL,14,FNottinghamshire Healthcare Trust was
OL,15,Fresponsible for both William Barnard,
OL,16,Fwho killed his grandfather in 2009,
OL,17,Fand also Valdo Calocane, who stabbed
OL,18,Fto death three people and seriously
OL,19,Finjured three others in Nottingham in
OL,20,F2023.
