OL,7,FBarnard was in the care of the Trust
OL,8,Fbecause of his deteriorating mental
OL,9,Fhealth. A review of the case in 2012
OL,10,Ffound he'd been failed by the
OL,11,Fauthorities and they promised lessons
OL,12,Fwould be learnt.
