OL,4,Ckilled grandfather say care failings
OL,5,Cpersist
OL,7,FThat comment was made once again by
OL,8,Fthe Trust yesterday following a
OL,9,Fdamning CQC report into the care of
OL,10,FCalocane, which showed that evidence
OL,11,F"indicated beyond any real doubt" that
OL,12,FCalocane would relapse "into
OL,13,Fdistressing symptoms and potentially
OL,14,Faggressive behaviour" yet he was
OL,15,Fdischarged back into the care of a GP.
