OL,5,Cpersist
OL,7,FKath Barnard, Barnard's mother said
OL,8,F"We've been here before and I know
OL,9,Fthey said they've put changes in place
OL,10,Fbut this was also said to us 15 years
OL,11,Fago and so I don't believe that that's
OL,12,Fthe case at all.
OL,14,F"Will was let down by them, ultimately
OL,15,Fthis ruined his life but also has
OL,16,Fimpacted on all our lives. He knows
OL,17,Fwhat he did and he has to live with
OL,18,Fthat guilt."
