OL,7,FThey pointed us to the statement
OL,8,Fissued following the Calocane Review
OL,9,Fin which they said they had
OL,10,Fsignificantly improved process and
OL,11,Fstandards, the Trust had a clear plan
OL,12,Fto address the issues highlighted, and
OL,13,Fwere doing everything in their power
OL,14,Fto understand where they missed
OL,15,Fopportunities and learn from them.
